msgctxt "an5.127:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.127:0.2"
msgid "13. Gilānavagga "
msgstr "13. Sick "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.127:0.3"
msgid "127. Vapakāsasutta "
msgstr "127. Living Apart "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#. VAR: vapakāsituṃ → vi + apa + kāsituṃ =
msgctxt "an5.127:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu nālaṃ saṃghamhā vapakāsituṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a mendicant with five qualities is not fit to live apart from a Saṅgha community. "

msgctxt "an5.127:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.127:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu asantuṭṭho hoti itarītarena cīvarena, asantuṭṭho hoti itarītarena piṇḍapātena, asantuṭṭho hoti itarītarena senāsanena, asantuṭṭho hoti itarītarena gilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārena, kāmasaṅkappabahulo ca viharati. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant is not content with any kind of robe, alms-food, lodging, and medicines and supplies for the sick. And they have a lot of sensual thoughts. "

msgctxt "an5.127:1.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu nālaṃ saṃghamhā vapakāsituṃ. "
msgstr "A mendicant with these five qualities is not fit to live apart from a Saṅgha community. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.146, sc2
msgctxt "an5.127:2.1"
msgid "Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu alaṃ saṃghamhā vapakāsituṃ. "
msgstr "A mendicant with five qualities is fit to live apart from a Saṅgha community. "

msgctxt "an5.127:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

#. VAR: nekkhammasaṅkappabahulo → na kāmasaṅkappabahulo (mr)
msgctxt "an5.127:2.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu santuṭṭho hoti itarītarena cīvarena, santuṭṭho hoti itarītarena piṇḍapātena, santuṭṭho hoti itarītarena senāsanena, santuṭṭho hoti itarītarena gilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārena, nekkhammasaṅkappabahulo ca viharati. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant is content with any kind of robe, alms-food, lodging, and medicines and supplies for the sick. And they think a lot about renunciation. "

msgctxt "an5.127:2.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu alaṃ saṃghamhā vapakāsitun”ti. "
msgstr "A mendicant with these five qualities is fit to live apart from a Saṅgha community.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.127:2.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

